  "definitions": {
    "c-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "ANIMATION PATTERN CATEGORIES",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.75rem"
    },
    "c-p1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Continuity Motion\n\n**Effect:** Reduces load ↓\n\nAnimations that preserve object identity across states — an element moving from one position to another rather than disappearing and reappearing.\n\nThe brain does not have to decide whether the new object is related to the old one.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-p2": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Causal Animation\n\n**Effect:** Reduces load ↓\n\nDirect visual feedback confirming that an action had an effect — a button press dimming, a form field flashing red on error, a card expanding on tap.\n\nEliminates the need for the user to infer whether anything happened.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.07
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-p3": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Entrance Animation\n\n**Effect:** Mixed / context-dependent\n\nElements appearing on page load. Useful when sequential presentation aids comprehension (progressive disclosure). Harmful when all elements animate simultaneously or delay access to content.\n\nRule: animate to reveal, not to display.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.14
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-p4": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Decorative Motion\n\n**Effect:** Adds load ↑\n\nMotion with no semantic relationship to content — background particle systems, hover effects that don't indicate interactivity, looping ambient animations.\n\nConsumed by pre-attentive vision automatically, regardless of whether the user wants to process them.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.21
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
